<P>THE ELEMENTS OF MEDICINE; OR, A TRANSLATION OF THE ELEMENTA MEDICINAE BRUNONIS.</P>
<P>WITH LARGE NOTES, ILLUSTRATIONS, AND COMMENTS.</P>
<P>BY THE AUTHOR OF THE ORIGINAL WORK.</P>
<P>A NEW EDITION.</P>
<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> PRINTED BY T. DOBSON, AT THE STONE-HOUSE, NO. 41, SECOND-STREET;</P>
